These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, dancing, singing, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, family, mystery
City: new-york, paris, nizza, berlin
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, blue, lilac, brown
 1. the person traveling to paris is not to the right of the person traveling to new-york##8
 2. the person who likes turquise is not to the left of the person who likes turquise##8
 3. the person who likes brown is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person traveling to new-york is not to the left of the person traveling to berlin##8
 5. the person who likes turquise is not to the right of the person who likes turquise##8
 6. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 8. the person watching mystery movies is between the person who likes blue and the person traveling to paris##2
 9. the person who likes brown is the person watching family movies##1
10. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
11. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
13. the person watching family movies is not to the left of the person who likes brown##8
14. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person who likes lilac##1
15. the person who's hobby is dancing is not the person traveling to paris##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | camping     | dancing   | woodworking | singing |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | mystery   | animation   | family  |
| City         | paris  | nizza  | berlin  | new-york |
| Color     | turquise    | lilac | blue     | brown    |

