.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
4 different games are played: snooker, scrabble, domino, backgammon
There 4 different types of food: carrot, grapes, kale, peas
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, indie, salsa, trance
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, taxi, skateboard, scooter
 1. the fan of salsa is between the person driving the car and the fan of indie##2
 2. the person playing scrabble is not to the right of the person driving the taxi##8
 3. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
 4. the person playing snooker is not to the right of the person driving the scooter##8
 5. the person driving the car is not to the left of the fan of indie##8
 6. the person eating peas is not to the right of the person playing backgammon##8
 7. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
 8. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of house is the person driving the taxi##1
10. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
11. the person driving the car is not to the left of the fan of salsa##8
12. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
13. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapes##5
14. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
15. the person playing snooker is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
17. the person playing snooker is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
18. the person eating grapes is not to the right of the person driving the taxi##8
19. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Game      | snooker | domino | backgammon  | scrabble  |
| Food          | peas     | grapes | carrot | kale  |
| Music-Genre   | indie    | salsa  | trance | house |
| Transport           | skateboard | scooter | car    | taxi  |

