 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the librarian##5
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the fan of blues##5
 5. the person who growslily is not to the right of the writer##8
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the software-developer##8
 7. the fan of folk is in an odd position##4
 8. the software-developer is on the left of the librarian##1
 9. the librarian is on the left of the manager##1
10. the person who growsdaisy is on the far right##1
11. the writer is not to the left of the fan of electronic##8
12. the librarian is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3

