.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-4::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, banana, cucumber, plum
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, chess, puzzles, reading
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, hot-chocolate, 7up
There are 4 different nationalities: french, dutch, brazilian, italian
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the person drinking coffee##6
 2. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
 3. the person eating plum is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 4. the person eating banana is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking fanta##2
 5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the french##3
 6. the french is not to the right of the person eating banana##8
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
 9. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the person drinking fanta is the french##1
11. the dutch is not to the right of the person eating apple##8
12. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the dutch##3
13. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
14. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the dutch##3
15. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Food    | cucumber    | banana             | apple   | plum     |
| Hobby   | board-games | puzzles            | reading | chess    |
| Beverage     | fanta | 7up | coffee  | hot-chocolate |
| Nationality   | french  | dutch               | brazilian  | italian   |

