 9. the british is not to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
10. the tower house is not to the left of the cottage house##8
11. the person drinking tea is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the craftsman house##2
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
13. the malaysian is not to the right of the craftsman house##8
14. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3

