.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-6::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, february, november, december
4 different games are played: scrabble, monopoly, bridge, billiard
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, dutch, nigerian, thai
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, scooter, van
 1. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5
 2. the person driving the bus is not to the left of the person playing billiard##8
 3. the person driving the bus is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##8
 4. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##5
 5. the person driving the scooter is the nigerian##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the right of the dutch##8
 7. the person who's birthday is in february is not the thai##6
 8. the person playing monopoly is somewhere between the person driving the scooter and the person who's birthday is in february##7
 9. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
10. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
11. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
12. the person playing monopoly is not the argentine##6
13. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5
14. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
15. the person driving the bus is not to the right of the person playing monopoly##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Birthday      | february    | december   | november        | march  |
| Game           | billiard     | monopoly | scrabble | bridge  |
| Nationality   | argentine | thai    | nigerian   | dutch     |
| Transport     | van       | bus     | scooter    | quad-bike |

