10. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4
11. the person who's birthday is in february is not to the left of the wooden house##8
12. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
13. the wooden house is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
14. the fan of folk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
