.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, dog, frog, goat
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, reggae, soul
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, lacrosse, tennis
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, video-games, skydiving, traveling
 1. the owner of the frog is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 3. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
 4. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 7. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
 8. the person who's hobby is video-games is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
10. the owner of the dog is not to the right of the fan of folk##8
11. the fan of reggae is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Pet      | rabbit   | goat     | frog    | dog |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | soul      | reggae     | folk     |
| Sport         | climbing | lacrosse  | tennis     | cycling  |
| Hobby     | card-games     | skydiving | traveling | video-games     |

