.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-17::.
House: wooden, art-deco, palace, cottage
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, chess, magic-tricks, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, water-polo, badminton, soccer
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, british, german, italian
 1. the wooden house is on the left of the italian##1
 2. the wooden house is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
 3. the cottage house is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
 5. the art-deco house is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##8
 7. the palace house is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
 8. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the german##3
 9. the british is not to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
10. the person who's sport is badminton is not the brazilian##6
11. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
12. the italian is on the left of the palace house##1
13. the person who's sport is soccer is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
14. the brazilian is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |      4       |
| House      | wooden      | cottage  | palace | art-deco        |
| Hobby         | skydiving | chess   | baking   | magic-tricks |
| Sport   | soccer    | water-polo   | badminton    | volleyball      |
| Nationality   | british   | italian | german   | brazilian    |

