.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-18::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, indie, techno
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, electrician, musician, police-officer
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, lilac, amber, mauve
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, scooter, subway, van
 1. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
 2. the person who likes mauve is not to the right of the electrician##8
 3. the person who likes brown is the fan of disco##1
 4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
 5. the fan of disco is somewhere to the right of the person who likes amber##5
 6. the person driving the van is the fan of electronic##1
 7. the police-officer is not to the right of the person driving the van##8
 8. the musician is on the far right##1
 9. the electrician is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
10. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
11. the person who likes brown is somewhere to the left of the person who likes mauve##5
12. the person who likes amber is somewhere to the left of the person who likes lilac##5
13. the person driving the subway is not to the left of the police-officer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1        |    2     |      3      |     4     |
| Music-Genre    | electronic          | disco | indie        | techno    |
| Job         | police-officer | doctor   | electrician | musician  |
| Color         | amber           | brown     | mauve       | lilac  |
| Transport   | van            | subway   | scooter     | quad-bike |

