.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, lemonade, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, card-games, puzzles, rock-climbing
House: gothic-revival, victorian, cottage, futuristic
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, january, june, september
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the person drinking lemonade##6
 2. the gothic-revival house is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##8
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 4. the gothic-revival house is not to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
 5. the victorian house is somewhere to the right of the cottage house##5
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 8. the person drinking coffee is not to the left of the cottage house##8
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
10. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in september and the futuristic house##7
11. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |      2       |       3       |    4    |
| Beverage    | lemonade        | fanta        | coffee        | water   |
| Hobby       | card-games      | camping      | rock-climbing | puzzles |
| House         | futuristic | cottage | victorian     | gothic-revival  |
| Birthday   | june          | march      | january     | september  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, collecting, singing, sudoku
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, juice, hot-chocolate, cola
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, romance, western
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, scooter, airplane, boat
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the person drinking water##8
 2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 3. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the right of the person driving the airplane##5
 4. the person drinking cola is the person watching western movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is not the person drinking hot-chocolate##6
 6. the person watching adventure movies is not to the right of the person driving the scooter##8
 7. the person watching animation movies is not to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
 9. the person driving the airplane is in an even position##4
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
11. the person watching adventure movies is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
13. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku    | singing   | board-games   | collecting |
| Beverage           | water | juice    | hot-chocolate | cola    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance   | adventure | animation     | western    |
| Transport   | jet-ski   | airplane      | scooter         | boat     |

 